    <item>
      <title>拜登将宣布十年内更换美国所有铅管的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/all-us-lead-pipes-to-be-replaced-in-decade-under-biden-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周二访问选举战场州威斯康星州时宣布一项计划，在未来 10 年内更换全国所有铅管，并承诺从环境保护署额外拨款 26 亿美元用于改善饮用水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/all-us-lead-pipes-to-be-replaced-in-decade-under-biden-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中欧关系恶化 中国调查欧盟汽车 并向白兰地征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在研究提高大引擎汽车的关税，并将开始对来自欧洲的白兰地征收关税，这在欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税后，加剧了贸易争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列国防部长将前往美国 回应伊朗问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-defense-chief-to-head-to-us-as-iran-retaliation-looms</link>
